# Placeholder Assets

This folder contains placeholder images for the Expo app. The `generate-assets.js` script in the parent directory will create these automatically when `npm install` is run via the `postinstall` hook.

If assets are missing, run:
```bash
node ../generate-assets.js
```

## Files needed:
- `icon.png` - App icon
- `splash.png` - Splash screen
- `adaptive-icon.png` - Android adaptive icon
- `favicon.png` - Web favicon

All are generated as minimal 1x1 transparent PNG files for development purposes.
